  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span class=3DSpellE>HyperDeny</span> components pre=
vent any
  ships within range from initiating a hyperjump. This prevents enemy ships
  from escaping battle, allowing an attacker to destroy them.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span class=3DSpellE>HyperDeny</span> components typ=
ically have
  high power requirements, and thus are usually found only on larger milita=
ry
  ships.</p>
